item.title: CVE-2024-22124|2024-01-09T01:19:55.940Z -- SAP_SE -- SAP NetWeaver (Internet Communication Manager)
item.description: Under certain conditions, Internet Communication Manager (ICM) or SAP Web Dispatcher - versions KERNEL 7.22, KERNEL 7.53, KERNEL 7.54, KRNL64UC 7.22, KRNL64UC 7.22EXT, KRNL64UC 7.53, KRNL64NUC 7.22, KRNL64NUC 7.22_EXT, WEBDISP 7.22_EXT, WEBDISP 7.53, WEBDISP 7.54, could allow an attacker to access information which would otherwise be restricted causing high impact on confidentiality.
